body:
When someone first mentioned the mage reworks in season 6, I was pretty hyped. Being a primarily mage player i was really excited to see the new items. And although i like how riot is bringing new aspects to the mid lane, i was more than a bit disappointed that there weren&#039;t any really high ratio AP items. And all the items had a lot of CDR, but not much AP. Being an offensive mage player i can say i am quite disappointed because riot is changing the items to be more utility focused. And i was really hoping for stuff like ludens echo, high AP ratio and a lot of fun. Seeing as though we have a lot of time because the reworks are coming out ages away, i would just like to reccomend that Riot make one or two offensive mage items. Because i feel like a lot of mages wont benefit from the low amounts of AP these items are given. I am really excited about what the new mages are going to be like though.
Just a suggestion
{{champion:103}}
